styleCard.description: A traditional tango piece, evoking the melancholic yet beautiful journey from the urban heart of Buenos Aires to the coastal serenity of Mar del Plata, filled with dramatic turns and reflective stretches.

directions: Start at Buenos Aires, Ciudad Autónoma de Buenos Aires
Go east on Avenida Hipólito Yrigoyen
At the traffic light, turn left on Avenida Belgrano
At the traffic light, continue forward on Calle Azucena Villaflor
At the traffic light, turn right on Avenida Ingeniero Huergo
Keep right to merge onto Autopista Buenos Aires La Plata (RN-01)
At the roundabout, take the first exit toward Acceso a Barrios
Finish at Calle Lorenzini 960, Mar del Plata, General Pueyrredón, B7606, Provincia de Buenos Aires, on the left
